[This may be the most western confirmed diagnosis of this disease. This disease clearly continues its march across the country and while there is some good news that some bats are recovering, overall this is a devastating disease. The enlargement of this disease's territory is also sad news.

Missouri may be found on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at: http://healthmap.org/r/3khV. - Mod.TG]

[For a map of Missouri showing counties, see http://www.digital-topo-maps.com/county-map/missouri.shtml. Crawford County is in the Southeastern part of Missouri, several counties to the southwest from Saint Louis county. - Mod.MPP]
